Wendy J. DEJANA
v.
Michael DEJANA Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided December 6, 2017

James H. Lee, in support of the petition.

Dori-Ellen S. Feltman, in opposition.

The plaintiff's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 176 Conn. App. 104, 168 A.3d 595 (2017), is denied.
